cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with automatic pain estimation from face videos, which involves computer vision and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves human-computer interaction (HCI) and medical applications, which could fall under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of deep learning techniques and the combination of hand-crafted features suggest that the paper could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
